"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1938541-novak-djokovic-billionaire-french-open-Ion-Tiriac-Olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Novak Djokovicmade a wager with French Open winner Ion Tiriac following his gold medal triumph at theOlympics,according to the formertennisstar.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 146, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 53, \"end\": 63, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ion_\\u021airiac\", \"score\": 0.9999996628212671, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ion Tiriac\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ion_\\u021airiac\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ion_\\u021airiac\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Serbian sporting icon made further history in his sport when defeating Carlos Alcaraz 7-6 7-6 in the gold medal match at the Paris Games earlier this month.\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 151, \"end\": 158, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"score\": 0.5490074716256559, \"rank\": 0.7957924896339247, \"text\": \"Serbian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia\"}, {\"begin\": 222, \"end\": 236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 37-year-old earned his first medal in Paris and became just the fifth player in tennis history to achieve a Golden Slam alongside Steffi Graff,Rafael Nadal, Andre Agassi and Serena Williams as the only players to win every Grand Slam and an Olympic gold medal.\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 351, \"end\": 356, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999997370982828, \"rank\": 2.62902418827521e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 443, \"end\": 455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steffi_Graf\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Steffi Graff\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steffi_Graf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steffi_Graf\"}, {\"begin\": 456, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 470, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andre_Agassi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andre Agassi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andre_Agassi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andre_Agassi\"}, {\"begin\": 487, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Serena Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serena_Williams\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On top of the rampant celebrations that surely would have followed after his narrow win over his Spanish rival, a wager between Djokovic and ex-tennis ace-turned-businessman Tiriac was said to have occurred during a phone call, with the billionaire Romanian making the claim during an interview withwelovetennis.\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"score\": 0.9991280688038148, \"rank\": 0.0004754957169314245, \"text\": \"Spanish\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spanish_language\"}, {\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999686224, \"rank\": 3.14280305360002e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 824, \"end\": 832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9943717206246085, \"rank\": 0.005576158228977356, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tiriac - who won the 1970 French Open in men's doubles - spoke of Djokovic's early start in tennis that saw him travel to Romania due to the expensive cost of playing the sport in his hometown of Belgrade.\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 955, \"end\": 963, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999686224, \"rank\": 3.14280305360002e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 1011, \"end\": 1018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"score\": 0.9979030754242454, \"rank\": 0.0019072217752073206, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\"}, {\"begin\": 1085, \"end\": 1093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgrade\", \"score\": 0.9999996098002464, \"rank\": 3.6624326977919945e-07, \"text\": \"Belgrade\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgrade\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"'Baby' Djokovic trained in Romania when he was just starting out, travelling 80 kilometres every day because it was too expensive in Belgrade,\\\" the 85-year-old said.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1122, \"end\": 1129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"score\": 0.9979030754242454, \"rank\": 0.0019072217752073206, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania\"}, {\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1236, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgrade\", \"score\": 0.9999996098002464, \"rank\": 3.6624326977919945e-07, \"text\": \"Belgrade\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgrade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgrade\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having made his billions in the banking industry before branching out into insurance, auto leasing, auto dealerships and airlines, Tiriac claimed to have made a bet with Djokovic after his stunning victory in Paris.\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1432, \"end\": 1440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999686224, \"rank\": 3.14280305360002e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 1471, \"end\": 1476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999997370982828, \"rank\": 2.62902418827521e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the billionaire, who has a reported net worth of up to $2.1bn (\\u00a31.6bn), was particularly coy on the details surrounding the supposed wager.\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I invited him to the Bucharest tournament twice.\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I know him well.\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's a very decent person.\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1716, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, I called him after his victory in Paris at the Olympic Games and told him: 'Young man, old player'.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1825, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1760, \"end\": 1765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999997370982828, \"rank\": 2.62902418827521e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I also took the opportunity to make a bet with him, but unfortunately I can not tell you more about that (laughs).\\\"\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Djokovic has a sizeable net worth of his own, supposedly of around \\u00a3180m from his tennis career and endorsements.\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1945, \"end\": 1953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999686224, \"rank\": 3.14280305360002e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the financial figures surrounding his and Tiriac's bet will remain a mystery.\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2252, \"to\": 2328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  In a prior interview, Tiriac was asked his thoughts onRoger Federerwho he revealed had always shown him the ultimate respect despite the pair not being overly familiar with each other.\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2570, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not actually knowRoger Federervery well, but he has always respected me.\", \"from\": 2571, \"to\": 2649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like the other stars on the circuit, he calls me the boss.\\\"\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tiriac admitted he believes the Swiss superstar belongs in a \\\"different category\\\" to Nadal and Djokovic, despite having less Grand Slams than both players.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2743, \"end\": 2748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_people\", \"score\": 0.5559969138543631, \"rank\": 0.7985708800854913, \"text\": \"Swiss\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swiss_people\"}, {\"begin\": 2796, \"end\": 2801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 2.9292153527837488e-12, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 2806, \"end\": 2814, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999686224, \"rank\": 3.14280305360002e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I honestly believe that he's really in a different category if you compare him to Nadal or Djokovic, for example.\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2950, \"end\": 2955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 2.9292153527837488e-12, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 2959, \"end\": 2967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999686224, \"rank\": 3.14280305360002e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's a player who has invented things on the tennis court that did not exist before.\", \"from\": 2982, \"to\": 3066, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Physically, he has always been a bit inferior to Djokovic and Nadal, but there is no doubt of his talent.\\\"\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3116, \"end\": 3124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"score\": 0.9999999999686224, \"rank\": 3.14280305360002e-11, \"text\": \"Djokovic\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novak_Djokovic\"}, {\"begin\": 3129, \"end\": 3134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999970441, \"rank\": 2.9292153527837488e-12, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q